[[Image:Income Education 91 to 03.jpg|thumb|450px|This graph shows the median household income in 2003 dollars according to educational attainment.<ref name="Educational attainment and median household income">{{cite web|url=http://www.census.gov/hhes/income/histinc/h13.html|title=Educational attainment and median household income|accessdate=2006-09-24}}</ref>]]
